{"tid":1134733,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"業主收回單位 六旬男租客情緒激動一度危坐窗邊","createTime":"2019-05-02T00:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T05:40:43.000Z","uid":46873,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bca5dc8b277db0935449a8bdbaf06cc04b790601","tid":1134733,"uid":46873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T00:59:22.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】青山公路葵涌段483號和記大厦A座17樓一單位，一名60多歲男租客因女業主收回單位發生爭執，一時情緒激動，踏出窗台危坐窗邊，經兩男女警員合力勸解，最後將他拉回屋內。<br />\n<br />\n　　事發中午近12時半，該名男租客情緒激動，女業主見狀報警。警員到場，由一名軍裝男警與女輔警進行勸解，見事主態度稍為軟化時，兩人即迅速上前將男子拉回屋內，過程中男租客擦傷面部，男警手部亦受輕傷，兩人毋須送院。該名男租客亦願意遷出單位，警方列作糾紛案處理｡"},{"pid":"8ad09d303658e1b0ad9475cf4b592111f819a1be","tid":1134733,"uid":83102,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"業主應該驚撚到鳩縮<br />\n一拉走佢即刻換鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad41f851896b709a5afa8896ef6ab1d40ab2a2e7","tid":1134733,"uid":4420,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8ad09d303658e1b0ad9475cf4b592111f819a1be","tid":1134733,"uid":83102,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"業主應該驚撚到鳩縮<br />\n一拉走佢即刻換鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:11:32.000Z","msg":"即刻換鎖唔得<br />\n可能要搵執達吏收左樓先"},{"pid":"8051cb538a1122a577f2f53f3060be3db057c96d","tid":1134733,"uid":144843,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:17:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f68114805ae19b4428984a74ffd84b78de64e491","tid":1134733,"uid":103921,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"連登廢淡將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話左租樓一身輕啦"},{"pid":"d96b3a324353ea884b83de086473b80c51f6b312","tid